{"tid":931330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<CIA> 張首晟自殺、孟晚舟被捕、ASML大火 幾乎同時發生  網友頻傳陰謀論","createTime":"2018-12-07T03:07:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T13:29:36.000Z","uid":62257,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6b3fa4a57242894ff3667938e3f02342a9fd34cf","tid":931330,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T03:07:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181207/1479613/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181207%2F1479613%2F&d=IrLFiNNngBdigec1cqo289U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=0775435d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181207%2F1479613%2F&h=62edcf72\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181207/1479613/</a><br />\n<br />\n中國科技大廠華為創辦人之女孟晚舟本月1日因涉嫌違反美國的伊朗制裁令而在加拿大遭逮捕。同一天，被中國列入「千人計劃」網羅人才名單的華裔物理學家張首晟在美國跳樓身亡。兩則看似不相關的新聞，看在中國大陸網友眼中卻是息息相關，懷疑張首晟之死很可能與華為有關。<br />\n<br />\n孟晚舟被捕和張首晟自殺的消息昨日同時曝光，而且兩件事都發生12月1日、美國總統川普和中國國家主席習近平在阿根廷G20舉行峰會的當天，看在中國大陸網友眼中覺得很不單純。有網友在微博發文：「劉強東、中興事件、孟晚舟、張首晟、科技界的一個接一個，是有人有意、設計的的嗎？！」另有網友指出12月1日當天，荷蘭光刻機巨頭ASML的元器件供應商發生大火也太過巧合，懷疑此事和美國圍剿中國晶片技術有關：「華為孟晚舟被抓、科學家張首晟自殺、荷蘭ASML工廠失火，真是細思極恐。」網路同時傳聞，張首晟可能有意與華為合作開發晶片，引發美方擔憂高科技外流。多維新聞網報導指，美國之所以要對中國加以警惕，是因為中國是最有潛力拿下5G技術的國家之一、中國是世界上推動5G商用進度最快的國家、美國在5G技術上已落後於中國。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"12fce25f5ee8e27cf47eb43a1ee790e982173d1a","tid":931330,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T03:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25143d2c89ae991a3842103375c8de13aa931d1b","tid":931330,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T03:13:36.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2879d3bd2f589a110a05b3c7b5bd7b842d9940e7","tid":931330,"uid":148332,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T03:14:28.000Z","msg":"美國外交部:我們促請各方停止無謂的猜測"},{"pid":"5300c8cbfdccc2d09b2a16788db10926f3ee9597","tid":931330,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T03:20:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c4f4fe9e06bfa6b1086c8846c84bcdca02b22a","tid":931330,"uid":14918,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T03:29:34.000Z","msg":"睇來斯諾登單野害死咁多OPS<br />\n而家終於回復元氣"},{"pid":"1969b8f51a8ea1e68f5ad8a6c449a1b1335a3b93","tid":931330,"uid":39365,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T03:44:10.000Z","msg":"其實真係好鬼, 孟晚舟果日由加拿大係飛去阿根庭見張首晟, 孟晚舟被人拉左後, 張首晟就跟住自殺, 我就唔相信巧合既, 當中實有事"},{"pid":"b2ae7715d5754a9a89b7b45df8c839bc7941e70d","tid":931330,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1969b8f51a8ea1e68f5ad8a6c449a1b1335a3b93","tid":931330,"uid":39365,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T03:44:10.000Z","msg":"其實真係好鬼, 孟晚舟果日由加拿大係飛去阿根庭見張首晟, 孟晚舟被人拉左後, 張首晟就跟住自殺, 我就唔相信巧合既, 當中實有事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T04:26:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd2101cd67617fdbd156424f2f5f8eecf83a4cb","tid":931330,"uid":59283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T04:28:20.000Z","msg":"剃人頭者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3394c52da005ea09c54b7e475e38d3b25ebf1ba2","tid":931330,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T04:28:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a19b190498149c8ade885345009222d11c90b1b","tid":931330,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T04:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4b7f12a10a34529bbc4bb7ad6585f79c61fc87","tid":931330,"uid":182499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T04:43:04.0