":93479,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T05:28:36.000Z","msg":"斷估<br />\n<br />\n張係中國間諜<br />\n將美國資料交畀孟<br />\n漏左風聲，美國拉孟<br />\n張畀人滅口"},{"pid":"06836f72e66a7264c88dfffd507bea0612544651","tid":931330,"uid":21896,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T05:31:43.000Z","msg":"張有機係比支那減聲減口"},{"pid":"f92012bafb71dfecb5d60a970d11873ade1b41dd","tid":931330,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06836f72e66a7264c88dfffd507bea0612544651","tid":931330,"uid":21896,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T05:31:43.000Z","msg":"張有機係比支那減聲減口"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T05:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef582f9b4cad9a8e2774eaf8cdb455217f2f92a2","tid":931330,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T06:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"381a4a4468d985e3fc3517f07b89a4e92fea33ec","tid":931330,"uid":31389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T06:47:47.000Z","msg":"佢地個世界觀係咁"},{"pid":"60a7287f7efffe6bd677da9e27ccff22933b0f66","tid":931330,"uid":21279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T06:48:50.000Z","msg":"3樣一齊黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e6fad97aac095776d70f72e0ac5b30b2abd260","tid":931330,"uid":189638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T10:30:36.000Z","msg":"完美支那世界觀<br />\n<br />\n但我又有另一睇法<br />\n<br />\n個物理學家已經被美國查緊，理由係偷取技術，間諜罪。<br />\n<br />\n所以係支那迫死佢比較合理，美國有反恐法，間諜罪係可以直接拉去監獄唔洗經法庭，唔洗司法程序。<br />\n<br />\n明知中興督華為背脊，供曬華為出嚟，美國仲要傳招過華為高層去解釋，但冇鳩人理。條友仲要用加拿大戶照係加拿大轉機？佢係專登比人捉去避難定真係咁唔小心？"},{"pid":"f0456f71034e65836e46324e88daacd16bd1de3d","tid":931330,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T13:27:11.000Z","msg":"啱啱我同老豆講開哩單野 老豆話美國拉完孟晚舟之後再殺果2個人 我同佢講果2條友係被中國政府搵殺手殺嘅 佢話我唔撚識政治 睇野太簡單...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}